metadata.name: Territorial Fight - Black Tailed Godwits
metadata.description:
Black tailed Godwits in a territorial fight. The species is a Near-Threatened species as per IUCN Red list.
Male Godwits fight each other to impress the females & to safeguard their territory
Location -Chilika lake, Odisha (RAMSER & UNESCO World Heritage Site)
Device - Nikon + Tamron
